<div id="outline-container-1-5-1-2-1" class="outline-6">
<h6 id="sec-1-5-1-2-1"><span class="section-number-6">1.5.1.2.1</span> Setup BOOTSTRAP</h6>
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-1-5-1-2-1">


<ul>
<li id="sec-1-5-1-2-1-1">Install Bootstrap<br/>

<ul>
<li><code>[&nbsp;]</code> Install the Bootstrap Gem 

<pre class="example">
gem 'bootstrap-sass'
</pre>


<pre class="example">
bundle install
</pre>


</li>
<li><code>[&nbsp;]</code> Create/add to app/assets/stylesheets/bootstrap<sub>and</sub><sub>customization</sub>.css.scss

<pre class="example">
@import 'bootstrap';
</pre>


</li>
<li><code>[&nbsp;]</code> Restart your server
</li>
</ul>


</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li id="sec-1-5-1-2-1-2">Add a container to our app<br/>

<ul>
<li><code>[&nbsp;]</code> modify app/views/layouts/application.html.erb, varying links as necessary

<ul>
<li>application.html.erb is a wrapper for each page

<pre class="example">
&lt;%= link_to "Home", root_path %&gt;
&lt;%= link_to "About", about_path %&gt;
&lt;%= link_to "Contact", contact_path %&gt;
&lt;%= link_to "Sign Up", sign_up_path %&gt;
&lt;%= link_to "Log In", log_in_path %&gt;
&lt;div class="container"&gt;
    &lt;%= yield %&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>


</li>
<li><code>[X]</code> <b>ERROR</b> SOLVED

<ul>
<li><code>[X]</code> When in doubt, check for outdated gems

<pre class="example">
bundle outdated
</pre>


