</pre>


<pre class="example">
undefined method 'environment' for nil:NilClass
 (in /home/son/RAILS-dev/son/nebraska-dating/app/assets/stylesheets/bootstrap_and_customizations.css.scss)
</pre>


<pre class="example">
&lt;%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" =&gt; true %&gt;
</pre>


<p>
         My first search found this stackoverflow post:
         <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/22392862/undefined-method-environment-for-nilnilclass-when-importing-bootstrap">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/22392862/undefined-method-environment-for-nilnilclass-when-importing-bootstrap</a>
</p>
<p>
         It seems to have something to do with a adding @import 'bootstrap': line
