<li id="sec-1-5-1-2-1-3">Create a <sub>header</sub>.html.erb Partial<br/>

<p>
       <a href="http://guides.rubyonrails.org/layouts_and_rendering.html">Layouts and Rendering</a>
</p>
<ul>
<li><code>[&nbsp;]</code> app/views/layouts/<sub>header</sub>.html.erb

</li>
